  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of lung aeration during weaning from mechanical ventilation determined by
      electrical impedance tomography and lung ultrasound
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective clinical study in ICU with patients during weaning from mechanical ventilation
      comparing lung aeration determined by electrical impedance tomography and lung ultrasound.

      Duration of weaning test is 60 minutes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
